ED_Title: Election of the United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees
ED_DecisionText: At its 14th plenary meeting, on 26 September 2022, the General Assembly, on the proposal of the Secretary-General (A/77/260), re-elected Filippo GRANDI (Italy) as United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees for a period of two and a half years, beginning on 1 July 2023 and ending on 31 December 2025.
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/77/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
